PEOPLE
v.
LESTER S214648 Supreme Court of California September 14, 2016 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Review in the above-captioned matter, which was originally granted and held for People v. Conley (2016) 63 Cal.4th 646, 203 Cal.Rptr.3d 622, 373 P.3d 435, is hereby dismissed. (See Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)

Corrigan, J., was absent and did not participate.
